---
title: One-Pan Turkey & Rice Skillet with Zucchini, Marinated Tomato & Lemon Garlic Sauce
description: You’ve heard of farm to table? This is “pan to table!” There’s nothing easier or more satisfying on a weeknight than digging into a bountiful skillet. This one features tender zucchini, savory turkey, and caramelized onion, infused with aromatic spices, and topped with a creamy lemon-garlic sauce and juicy marinated tomatoes. Best of all, it’s ready in just 30 minutes!
